{"tid":969562,"cid":7,"subCid":0,"title":"BLACKPINK JENNIE爆出戀情後首露面！","createTime":"2019-01-05T07:05:24.000Z","updateTime":"2019-01-05T08:00:06.000Z","uid":74065,"like":1,"dislike":8,"uniUserReply":13,"replies":[{"pid":"44ab83df60ce4a11471fa564a734dbc1e14255e5","tid":969562,"uid":74065,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-01-05T07:05:24.000Z","msg":"JENNIE爆出戀情後首露面！BLACKPINK拍照全僵在台上<br />\n<br />\n南韓金唱片獎音源部門今（5）天下午轉播，2019年第一天爆出的偶像情侶檔女主角JENNIE也與BLACKPINK成員一起踏上紅毯，不知道是否受到緋聞影響，4人看起來特別緊張，連打招呼口號都沒喊，JENNIE則以淺淺微笑回應鏡頭。<br />\n<img src=\"https://cdn2.ettoday.net/images/3812/d3812660.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fcdn2.ettoday.net%2Fimages%2F3812%2Fd3812660.jpg&h=5e89f6a8&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n▲JENNIE（左二）爆出戀情後首露面。（圖／翻攝自vlive）<br />\n<br />\n金唱片在台灣時間下午2點就舉行，BLACKPINK被安排第3組走紅毯，4人排排站在媒體面前，擺出pose顯得有點僵硬，面部表情也相對其他偶像比較沒有燦爛笑容，1月1日被爆出正在與EXO成員KAI戀愛的JENNIE，身穿白色禮服，僅以淡淡的微笑面向媒體。<br />\n<img src=\"https://cdn2.ettoday.net/images/3812/d3812659.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fcdn2.ettoday.net%2Fimages%2F3812%2Fd3812659.jpg&h=784bd146&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n▲BLACKPINK面對拍照，顯得特別僵硬。（圖／翻攝自vlive）<br />\n<br />\n不僅如此，BLACKPINK的紅毯也特別簡短，主持人把麥克風交給Jisoo，請她們對鏡頭打個招呼，前面走紅毯的偶像們都會先唸出團體的打招呼口號，但BLACKPINK 4人沒有一起喊出來，而是由Jisoo簡短祝福大家新年快樂。<br />\n<img src=\"https://cdn2.ettoday.net/images/3812/d3812661.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fcdn2.ettoday.net%2Fimages%2F3812%2Fd3812661.jpg&h=9223f636&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n▲Jisoo代替BLACKPINK簡短發言。（圖／翻攝自vlive）<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/36.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/36.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/36.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/36.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/36.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"9728518d4dbef6bc320d39927a07faef8e4bb75a","tid":969562,"uid":223790,"like":7,"dislike":3,"score":4,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-01-05T07:05:39.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"66a4a746c0dc0fb502010b9176ba90823e401981","tid":969562,"uid":223790,"like":12,"dislike":3,"score":9,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-01-05T07:07:02.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"c5d8c1f115757ef65dff5f98c1c8191612ed83f9","tid":969562,"uid":223790,"like":5,"dislike":16,"score":-11,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-01-05T07:10:37.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"1e358327990d8d2c6d61fccdf52f18987c449620","tid":969562,"uid":191352,"like":0,"dislike":2,"score":-2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-01-05T07:10:45.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"79c17af6de556aff63231a2344fcf71d98156d8c","tid":969562,"uid":223790,"like":2,"dislike":12,"score":-10,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-01-05T07:10:55.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"0dfe741cb54f6f77eb20b436e904008a8ba7daad","tid":969562,"uid":46435,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-01-05T07:11:34.000Z","msg":"Jennie大波波"},{"pid":"0e1e1786f3b76fa721774a8e1bae1617b9030fda","tid":969562,"uid":29606,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-01-05T07:11:54.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"ba309c1524996b488ffed24a29924c7a987cd5cb","tid":969562,"uid":223790,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-01-05T07:12:26.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"858ad68fd252c2063dd24371fd4729fd9e063bc7","tid":969562,"uid":29606,"like":2,"dislike":3,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-01-05T07:12:34.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"2b1ec2559dbdb79675a152eee83a62e16c9ef285","tid":969562,"uid":29606,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-01-05T07:13:02.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"955b83979904284c63052c04bac17a281c3886a1","tid":969562,"uid":223790,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-01-05T07:13:25.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"2db317635e3e69ca9b7f84b7831ce3e9c09280f2","tid":969562,"uid":52122,"like":6,"dislike":7,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-01-05T07:14:17.000Z","msg":"繼續jer住佢啦<br />\n唔好再搞twic